super sultry waves and curls to last all day.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-68_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-70_">The fishtail</span></h3><div title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-71_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-9371cb90--blog-in-4_1200x.jpg?v=1588869168" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-9371cb90--blog-in-4.jpg?v=1588869168 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls"/></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-72_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-74_">The <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href=""> fishtail</a></span> is one of our all-time favourite hairstyles, so we can’t help but include it here. It can be incorporated in so many different ways. There’s the double fishtail, the half up half down fishtail, and the upside fishtail. For a super easy style though, take a small section of hair from one side of your head and create a long, but thin, braid. For extra boho appeal, you can even add beads or a quirky ribbon. <p> </p></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-75_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-77_">The ballerina bun</span></h3><div title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-78_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-e19371cb--blog-in-3_1200x.jpg?v=1588869161" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-e19371cb--blog-in-3.jpg?v=1588869161 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls"/></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-79_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-81_">This gorgeous style can be achieved with <a href="https://www.cliphair.co.uk/collections/clip-in-hair-extensions" target="_blank">clip in hair extensions</a>, because it rewards body and volume. It’s also pretty easy to put together, if you can get a handle on the tricky tucking in bits. Once your extensions are secure, pull all of your hair into a ponytail that sits right at the top of your head (it should be really high). Backcomb the ends until they’re nice and fluffy. Then, in sections, curl them into a circular shape, with the ends secured at the stem of the ponytail; secure tightly with slides or grips. Alternatively, you can also get this style using <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href=""> ponytail hair extensions</a></span>. <p> </p></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-82_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-84_">The braided updo </span></h3><div title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-85_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-71cb90fd--blog-in-5_1200x.jpg?v=1588869174" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-71cb90fd--blog-in-5.jpg?v=1588869174 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls"/></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-86_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-88_">This simple, elegant braided updo is easy to achieve, you just have to braid two small sections at each side of your head and then gently pull all of your hair into a sleek bun. If you have longer hair, you can get away with pulling half of your tresses into a thick fishtail braid, and the other half into loose and romantic bun or top knot. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-89_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-91_">The uptown messy bun</span></h3><div title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-92_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-90fd316a--blog-in-7_1200x.jpg?v=1588869186" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0069/6470/7389/t/9/assets/pf-90fd316a--blog-in-7.jpg?v=1588869186 1536w" width="1080" height="1080" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" alt="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls" title="Top 7 Work-Approved Hairstyles Ideas for Video Conference Calls"/></div><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-93_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-95_">Thought that messy buns were only for weekends? Wrong! This version of a messy bun is created to look fashionably textured rather than overtly scruffy so your boss or client won’t criticize, and you will still look fab and feel great. You can either begin by adding your Cliphair extensions now or at the second stage of this look. If you are using your clip in hair extensions, you may find it more subtle to add your extensions at the second stage. <p> </p>

